This backlog project is a python project

It exposes endpoints.Behing the endpoint python scripts will perform some CRUD data

The database used is a document oriented one (NoSQL) mongodb

Here is the list of endpoint exposed by the API:

/parseBacklog (GET)

/AddBugOrTaskToEpic (POST)

databasese update

parameters

'condition' : it is a filter exemple {"Name" : "EpicC"}
'new_value' : the update statement example {"Epics": ["ba"]}
 
 ex: http://127.0.0.1:5000/AddBugOrTaskToEpic?condition='{"Name" : "EpicC"}'&new_value='{"Epics": ["ba"]}'

/ListAllBugsFromEpic (GET)

/ListAllBlockedEpicsFromBugNames (GET)

